						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: Śaka 1105, <hi rend="italic">Viśvāsu</hi>,</hi></p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record refers to certain epithets and mention is made of Oṟaiyūr. A certain Māchidēva is also referred to and he seems to have waged a war, the details of which are, however, not available. Two persons Bayireya and Bōvaṇa are mentioned.</p>						

